ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of KONRAD von FINCKENSTEIN of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of KONRAD von FINCKENSTEIN to be Chairperson of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission.
